review.reviewBody: Absolutely beautiful laptop stand for my setup. I use it for my work laptop and my MacBook. It cleaned up my desk, which is mounted in my dining room, and added a refined look. The walnut almost perfectly matches the wood of my desk (differences in finishes aside; I can't expect the seller to use tung oil). The included woolen strips help to make each slot perfect for my laptops, both my chunky government one and my thin MBP. The stand hasn't moved, so whatever they put on the bottom to keep it in place is great. Highly recommend this.

I was so impressed with my desk shelf from Oakywood that I decided to supplement my desk setup with a dual laptop stand to place my personal and work laptops. The stand is well built and looks very sturdy and elegant on the desk. Definitely a great purchase and would really recommend Oakywood to anyone else that wants to spice their desk/home office setup.

Beautiful carved wood stand for my laptop and tablet. The walnut is true to color as the online photos, and it looks great on my glass top desk. It comes nicely packaged from a US-based shipping point (so it arrived quickly) and came with clear instructions and plenty of soft wool strips to ensure a proper fit. I'm now eyeing a wood monitor stand from Oakywood.
It’s beautifully made and helps me reduce the clutter that was my desk! Love it

review.reviewBody: First off, I would like to say that I have been in search of new office products for the last two months because I am in the middle of re-doing my home office. I was debating on the wooden laptop riser from Grovemade and this laptop stand. I chose this laptop stand because I felt it was better looking than the Grovemade product, the wood on this one popped more and once I received the product from Oakywood, I was not disappointed at all. This laptop riser/stand is very high quality, I was very impressed with the packaging as well, they definitely take great pride in their products at Oakywood. Although I am not keeping the product, it is not because I do not like it, it's because, for the height of my desk, the stand holds my laptop up too high for my height and I end up looking up a little too much. Customer service is great!

I often get get things online, and in some way I get my money's worth, but never beyond my expectations. until today. 
I gifted my husband a desk, with a laptop wooden stand, Felt and Cork Desk Mat, headphone stand, dual  laptop and the desk shelve. 
First, I was very impressed with the packaging. I thought it look incredibly stylish, but then I opened every single item. Stylish is a understatement. 
The desk is the most beautiful piece of wood work I have ever seen. EVERY SINGLE PIECE IS AMAZING. My husband was speechless and then who would not stop talking about the perfection and beauty of every single thing I got him. 
it is my pleasure to give this company a 5 star review. it is more than well deserve. this are not pieces of furniture. this is ART. 
THANK YOU. 
Maria.

I literally JUST received this and already it feels amazing to me. It's very sturdy and done with such great care and is such great quality, it feels like it will last a lifetime. Definitely highly recommend.
Absolutely beautiful craftsmanship, packaged really neatly and it arrived super fast. My neck and back are very grateful for this addition to my work space.

name: Laptop Stand, Fold Away Bed Tray, Real Wood, Portable Foldable Lap Desk, Breakfast Serving Tray, Multifunctional Stand, Work From Home Gift
description:
★ MULTI-PURPOSE LAPTOP TRAY - This wood laptop table is designed to easily use your laptop in bed, seat, travel and anywhere you want. It can be an activity table for children, a breakfast tray in bed or a computer stand, a food tray while doing crafts or on the sofa. The wood laptop table has 2 different size options to choose according to your need. This versatile laptop tray will be indispensable! 

● FOLDABLE DESIGN - The portable laptop desk has a foldable design. This way, when not in use, you can easily store it without taking up too much space. At the same time, the edges of the product are designed to be curved so as not to harm you. Curved edges, functionality and ergonomic design will make your use easier. 

● AIRFLOW & HUMAN HEALTH - For the health of your laptop, there are holes that allow airflow to ensure that your laptop receives air and does not shorten its life. At the same time, this laptop stand is designed to keep your laptop at the right height. Correct posture when working on your laptop is crucial for both your spine health and your neck health. Thanks to this laptop stand, you will experience healthy laptop use. 

● QUALITY LAP DESK & SAFETY WOOD - Our real wood products are coated with natural teak oil, a nourishing and protective oil that penetrates deeply into the wood, giving it water repellent properties. There are no additives in our wood products. Applied teak oil has permission to be applied in children's toys. En 71/3 Standard (Safety of Toys/Migration of some Elements) 

● BENEFITS OF WOOD & GIFT Research on the effect of wood clearly shows that the presence of wood has positive effects; it lowers blood pressure, pulse and stress compared to other materials. It has a positive effect on one's emotional state. So this wooden laptop stand is a very nice gift for you and your loved ones!
